Hello everyone! @memyselfandsteph_ here’s a little mermaid magic that I #MadeWithPhotoshop⁠
⁠
Finding Photoshop was a real creative game-changer for me. It was the first time I really ever felt like an artist. Photoshop supplied me with all the tools I needed to bring my crazy imagination to life and it blew my mind. ⁠
⁠
Suddenly a world of possibilities was open to me and I poured my heart and soul into creating out-of-this-world pieces that satisfied my weird and wonderful ideas. And for this, I’ll always be grateful to Photoshop.⁠
⁠
How did Photoshop affect your creative journey? Let me know in the comments!⁠
⁠
And don’t forget to head over to Photoshop’s stories to see the tap-to-edit of this piece!⁠
